revision.text:
'''Gyms''' are special areas in Pokéclicker where the player can earn gym badges and unlock new routes by defeating the gym leader in a battle. There are 8 gyms in each region plus the Pokémon League building, which includes the Elite 4 trainers and the champion. [[File:Badge case.png|thumb|350px]]
